    <div id="myStory" class="contentSection">
        <h2 class="w-border">My Story</h2>
        <div class="paraWrap">
            <p>
                I’m a senior-level executive with more than 25 years of experience in finance, administration, IT, and
                human
                resource across multiple industries in both private and public sectors, including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>technology</li>
                <li>health care,</li>
                <li>lease/asset financing</li>
                <li>manufacturing</li>
                <li>warehouse/distribution</li>
            </ul>
