                professional
                experience and network of resources to your organization.Depending on your needs, I can scale
                time
                up or
                down, and can work in-person at your office or remotely.
            </p>
            <p>
                My goal is to help you achieve yours.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{end}}
    {{if eq .Page.Title "Home"}}
    <a href="/about" id="myStorybtn" class="btn secondary">Learn More</a>
    {{end}}
</div>
